words: I just got on Facebook one day, and I saw that, like, I saw pictures

I don't know how I feel about this 'cause, like, you don't really know her and stuff like

Um, and I don't know. I think it's
still something that I think about and feel badly about 'cause, um, I haven't talked to
him in almost a year now. Um, but I know that
he's, like, um, s-since getting married, he, like, got a green card, and she's over here,

I'm still feeling some type of way, and haven't really talked to him about it, so that's weird.
